window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Sol will ascend to the next level!!</b></p> <p>The war reached a lull. Sol forced a temporary ceasefire after defeating three of the Great Sages under Sun Wukong by himself.</p> <p>Now only seven days are left before the final Battle. A direct clash that will oppose him and his harem to Lupus and Sun Wukong.</p> <p>Failure is not an option.</p> <p>From preparing secret rituals, to learning news techniques and even making pact with previous enemies. He will use everything at his disposal.</p> <p>But will this be enough? What will be his True Name? And what price will he have to pay to obtain it?</p>"; 
